msgstr "安全"

#: src/Settings/Settings_Tabs.php:945
msgid "Bot mitigation and abuse protection."
msgstr "机器人缓解和滥用防护。"

#. translators: %s: link to the Captcha settings sub-section.
#: src/Settings/Settings_Tabs.php:962
